The paper deals with visual object tracking and multiple object tracking, which are both subfields of computer vision (cs.CV). The application domain is urban mixed traffic, which suggests robotics (cs.RO) as another likely sub-category. The paper also mentions background subtraction, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM). The use of KCF and data association also suggests machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as possible sub-categories.
